<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui" xmlns:c="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.cellview.client"
	xmlns:s="urn:import:org.sagebionetworks.web.client.view">

	<ui:style>
		.important {
		font-weight: bold;
		}

		.rowTop {
		vertical-align: top;
		}
	</ui:style>

	<g:HTMLPanel>
		<div class="color-line"></div>
		<g:SimplePanel ui:field="header" />
		<div class="separator margin-top-10-imp"></div>
		<div class="container">
			<ul class="breadcrumbs">
				<li>
					<a href="#!Home:0">Home</a>
					> All Projects
				</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="well margin-top-15">
				<g:SimplePanel ui:field="createProjectPanel" />
			</div>

			<h2>What is a Synapse Project?</h2>
			<h5>
				Projects are a great place to organize your work. Here
				are a few things you
				can do with a Synapse Project:
			</h5>
			<div class="row margin-top-15">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Organize Your Work</h4>
							<p>With Synapse you can organize the parts in your workflow
								(data,
								code, etc) into a hierarchy like a file system.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Organize.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Store Data, Code &amp; Results</h4>
							<p>You can upload your data, code and results to Synapse, or
								simply
								store a reference to where they are on your local computer
								system.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_StoreData.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Set Sharing Level</h4>
							<p>You have complete fine-grained control over how users and
								groups
								can interact with your work. Work privately or collaborate
								openly,
								and everything in between.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Acl.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Custom, Searchable Annotations</h4>
							<p>Assign any key/value pair you want, and those values become
								searchable and available to those granted access to see.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Annotations.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Full Programmatic API &amp; R Integration</h4>
							<p>Synapse is built on a REST API, so you can interact with
								Synapse
								using any programming language. We have built out full
								featured
								clients for R and Java.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_R.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Attach Figures and Documents</h4>
							<p>Upload documents and images via the website or
								programmatically.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Attachments.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Describe &amp; Version</h4>
							<p>Describe each of the elements in your workflow, and then
								version
								those when you see fit. This allows you to explicitly
								record which
								version of the code you ran on which version of the
								data.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Describe.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="well display-table">
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
							<h4 class="colored">Create Links &amp; See Usage</h4>
							<p>See some data stored elsewhere on Synapse? Make a link to
								store
								it in your project. Want to see what projects are using your data?
								They are displayed automatically.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
							<img class="img-preview spec-border" src="images/ProjectOverView_Links.png"
								alt=" " />
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- start footer -->
			<div class="clear"></div>
		</div> <!-- close class="container" -->
		<g:SimplePanel ui:field="footer" />
		<!-- end footer -->

	</g:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 